Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chiha-main,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:04.49,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.57,chalkboard,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Chemistry Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:08.57,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Pass your tests forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:15.53,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Exams are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:19.30,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Three days left until the Eastern qualifier!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:25.75,Chiha-title,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1700,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:34.17,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,The English essay was a cinch this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.67,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  It was a trick question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.57,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  A trick question?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:42.58,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)}Verse 21
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:42.58,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)}While \NSnow \NFalls \NUpon \NMy \NSleeves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:40.68,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It was written like you were \Nsupposed to give the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:41.96,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was really asking for the speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:42.58,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:44.58,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:54.21,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,the thistle and brush are \Nblown by the autumn wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:48.52,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, they're already at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.48,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,You can't blame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:54.21,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan never mentioned \Nkaruta during exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:56.64,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Must have taken some \Nserious self-control...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:03.57,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,My life means nothing after all \Nthe agonizing I have endured,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:01.09,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!  Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.42,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, when Ayase loses a card,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:08.49,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,she starts shaking her head,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:10.37,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,but she's just staring at the cards now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:13.48,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Like water...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.15,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Flowing seamlessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:24.21,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,How can I achieve that sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.54,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:29.67,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,That took forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.25,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you start without us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.62,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:33.88,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You're playing me next!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.00,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's play!  Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.54,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun, we're the other pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:38.44,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:40.13,Chiha-overlap,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to do the reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:39.48,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Need a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:46.54,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I love karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:51.85,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta brought Arata back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:57.61,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Since nationals last summer, Chihaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.16,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,always seemed so frantic \Nduring practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.81,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because she saw Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.95,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Man, why can't I get over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:12.41,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I can still change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:21.28,Chiha-poem,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, now the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:26.81,Chiha-poem,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Note that though we may be apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:31.98,Chiha-poem,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sound of someone knocking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:41.90,Chiha-poem,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,the thistle and brush are \Nblown by the autumn wind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:51.80,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Look for the sound of the cuckoo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.42,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.54,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.75,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to push yourself so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:02.44,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Humans aren't supposed to be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.18,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did I make any mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.68,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You were perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.66,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:10.12,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you notice, Chihaya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:13.25,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima-kun was reading all \Nof the cards from memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:13.66,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.12,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,He was randomly reading cards \Nwithout looking at anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:17.27,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,All from his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:17.91,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:22.05,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I read that this helps \Nimprove your memorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:24.45,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He randomly read all one hundred \Npoems without doubling up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.16,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.17,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your strength and weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.45,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You only see the words in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.45,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.45,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to know what's been read,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:38.40,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,but you have to feel \Nthe cards on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.21,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Use your eyes and treat them as images!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.59,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You never practice swinging because \Nyou think it's embarrassing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:46.74,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You need to learn the distance \Nbetween yourself and the cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:49.41,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You're playing karuta with \Nboth your mind and your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.66,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Mind and body...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:57.10,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I want to move faster, \Nbut my arm can't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.52,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get better with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:03.01,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to play in the \NEastern qualifier together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.62,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,So what I'm saying is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:12.17,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't need to memorize everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.45,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  How am I supposed to win then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.79,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You need to find your groove.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:19.54,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I only memorize the initial positions \Nfor about half the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.04,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'd be too scared of making a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.74,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.95,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:27.70,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Empress...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:29.78,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to your teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:32.93,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and you didn't fail any \Nof your exams this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:35.68,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't have to yell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:35.68,Chiha-overlap,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,That's marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.94,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck at the Queen qualifier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:55.70,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:57.92,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,...love karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:00.89,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:11.26,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Chihaya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:15.09,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We prepared a new hakama for \Ntoday's Eastern qualifier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:16.27,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.29,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:20.59,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but the heat works \Nagainst us in this tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.39,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,She won't be wearing a hakama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:23.02,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:26.70,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Most tournaments take place \Nin air-conditioned rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.58,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,but the windows here remain shut,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:31.22,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,and there are no fans,\N let alone air conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.99,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,So it's ridiculously hot in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.28,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:37.04,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Because every sound matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.56,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:44.55,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him with some \NSuihoku society members.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:50.13,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You and Komano ended up \Njoining the Suihoku society?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.80,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they've been helping us a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.93,sign-on-wood,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Suihoku Karuta Society
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.68,sign-on-wood,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Shiranami Karuta Society
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.44,shiranami,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Shiranami Karuta Society
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.44,suihoku,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Suihoku Karuta Society
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:06.94,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,They must have some history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.08,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.35,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,really focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.49,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.70,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully, she'll make \Nit past the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:29.72,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:33.35,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,It's the person who lost \Nto the Queen by 20 cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.60,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sudo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:38.79,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a third-year?\NDon't you need to study for college exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.93,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.22,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since my first choice is a \Nnational-level public school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:46.11,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,Though I managed to place second \Nfor the high school scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.71,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,High school scholarship?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:50.86,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:56.99,famous,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Famous Universities
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:54.33,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,If you come in first or second at \Nthe high school tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.99,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,you'll get scholarships \Nto famous universities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:08:00.95,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,I should also mention that the Queen \Ngets scholarships to good schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:58.68,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Famous universities
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.77,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:09.80,Queen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:09.80,karuta,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta Karuta\NKaruta Karuta
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:09.80,college,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,College
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:09.80,Scholarship,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Scholarship
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:09.80,daddybear,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy Bear
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.12,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.12,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He's got Chihaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.68,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,...thinking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:09.48,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,...unrelated topics!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.76,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.76,heartstrings,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Super\NSadist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.86,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like you have a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.13,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Wakamiya Shinobu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.60,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,might be a stronger player \Nthan the current Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.18,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see yourself beating her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:23.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:26.03,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's make a bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:29.07,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever loses first today \Nhas to shave their head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:31.89,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.07,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:36.13,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.13,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,A girl shaving her head is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:39.56,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,completely different from \Na guy shaving his head,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.40,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,and he's not going to take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.60,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.46,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,You just accidentally threw \Naway every girl's glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.69,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The opening ceremony is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:51.13,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She was all focused,\N but now it's been ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:58.27,Chiha-internaloverlap,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Accidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.92,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Will all of the players please assemble?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:55.51,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a beautiful day for karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:09:00.49,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Western qualifier is currently \Nbeing played at Omi Jingu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.80,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,If you become the best player in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.00,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be the best in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.28,Chiha-flashback,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That makes you the Queen, Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.03,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,In November, the East\N and West qualifier winners
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.11,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,will play each other in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:15.59,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.38,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.14,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Check the scorecard and sit \Ndown at your assigned location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.62,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up against...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:25.10,List,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Sudo Akito\NNishida Yusei
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.12,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Ack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.03,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,Burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.79,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.97,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defend your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:34.31,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:35.80,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You're also up against a tough opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:41.99,List,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase Chihaya\NTachikawa Ririka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,A tough opponent? \N What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.35,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You have no clue, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.01,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:44.23,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ririka-chan, can you pose for the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.24,Chiha-overlap,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Tachikawa Ririka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.52,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:45.55,Chiha-overlap,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,She's from Sendai,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:46.44,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:48.54,Chiha-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,and she made Class A as a fourth \Ngrader, just like the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.52,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,No worries, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.15,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,You also placed at the tournament \Nin Chiba last summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:52.00,Chiha-overlap,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,They're saying that she's \Nthe next Wakamiya Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.40,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,The child prodigy Ririka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.94,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ririka, your ribbon's loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:57.16,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,The expectations for her are huge,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.91,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,while most people don't \Neven know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:09.04,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,She's a speedy sixth grade star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.06,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:13.77,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:14.59,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:18.44,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,Someone told me that you're really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:20.34,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we have a good match today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:23.83,heartstrings,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Heartstrings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.77,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're too kind! \NI hope I don't disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.95,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.  There are so \Nmany matches being played
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.42,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that we need spectators to remain outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:34.28,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.06,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Ririka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.06,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:39.74,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.76,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The child prodigy Ririka...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.88,Chiha-flashback,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,The expectations for her are huge,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.88,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,while most people don't \Neven know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.08,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm expecting a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:00.36,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Dr. Harada, shouldn't you be inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:02.22,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I get a bye in the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.28,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,We get to save our energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:05.96,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  You too, Hiroshi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:06.77,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:10.71,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chihaya-chan's playing \NTachikawa Ririka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.47,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you think she'll do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:14.64,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,She won't lose to a grade schooler, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:20.41,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, you told\N Chihaya-chan to stop using
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:22.26,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,her speed to take cards, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:25.70,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it a little early to tell her that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:34.19,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Here comes spring, now the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:31.88,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan's strength will \Nalso be her game sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:34.09,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,She was making big strides,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:37.01,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,but now you've taken away her best weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.84,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when you consider that \Nshe's up against Tachikawa Ririka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:45.99,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Here comes spring, now the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:55.11,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,When I must hide these burning feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.46,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Good, Ririka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.86,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,As friends and strangers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.61,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,I know that my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:58.61,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's so light!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.61,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Swift waters parted...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:02.03,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's so light,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.91,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,even when she moves with her entire body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.12,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.24,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's not scared of committing faults,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:10.00,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,and her hearing is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:13.02,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ririka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:16.75,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Her ears are big like mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:17.93,Chiha-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Show us your ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.19,Chiha-flashbackinternal,,0000,0000,0000,,so kids used to tease her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.19,Chiha-flashback,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:22.18,Chiha-flashback,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, do my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.29,Chiha-flashback,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,The karuta coach said \Nthat I have good hearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.55,Chiha-flashback,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,My ears are really sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.91,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,If karuta's what you need...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.38,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ririka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:36.90,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.35,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She's faster than Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.78,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.40,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya moved back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:56.04,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,I deflect your artful words \Nto keep my sleeves dry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:04.11,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,After I determined to abandon \Nmy love, my only regret
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:59.53,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,is that I have no way \Nto tell you in person
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.01,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:04.10,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I matched the reader's timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:08.89,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:15.70,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,is that I have no way to tell you in person
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:12.14,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on timing instead of speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.61,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple task for some people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:16.80,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but not for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:23.23,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,So the flower petals are scattered \Nlike the snow by the passing storm,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:22.14,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making progress!  Improving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.74,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Though it may seem mundane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.99,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,She got the card, but she's slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.94,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,She got the card, but she's slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.68,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,She got the card, but she's slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:44.00,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,yet it is I who withers and wilts
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:40.42,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:43.90,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:46.18,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can understand how she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:52.77,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The emotions experienced \Nafter a long-awaited reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:55.48,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's happy to be playing \Nagainst grown-ups,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:59.50,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,and it's fun when people \Nsay that she's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:08.48,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,banish any lingering memories of the past
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:16.77,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,While it may be beyond my ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.24,Chiha-card-TS,N,0000,0000,0000,,and I have yet to visit Amanohashidate \Nor read my mother's letters
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.99,Chiha-internal,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,I committed a fault on a dead card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.73,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Ririka-chan \Nis dominating the match,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.50,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,but she doesn't have much of a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:20.56,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,Her opponent is reacting well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.75,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,Which society is that girl from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:30.30,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Ririka-chan was definitely \Ntargeting this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.62,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,and I have yet to visit Amanohashidate \Nor read my mother's letters
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.25,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send it and take it from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.39,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pick up every card \Nthat Ririka-chan doesn't target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.07,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:40.80,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Take each card at the perfect time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.78,Chiha-flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.09,Chiha-flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,I get to play a girl who only has speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:49.81,Chiha-flashback,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, stop taking \Ncards with your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.34,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.53,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Ririka-chan in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:15:00.53,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Her opponent doesn't seem that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:02.84,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,So much for being a prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.13,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan is setting a good pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.12,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,If she's careful, she can pull this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:10.54,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,If she takes her time, her \Nopponent will make mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:11.93,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.39,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:15.10,Chiha-overlap,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:22.23,speed,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,You
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:22.98,speed,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,You can
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:23.73,speed,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,You can use
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:24.36,speed,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,You can use your
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.11,speed,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,You can use your speed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:25.61,speed,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,You can use your speed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.36,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,"You can use your speed now"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:36.32,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Should I trust Doctor Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:52.22,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,I volunteer to shield the \Npeople with my dark sleeves
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:16:02.01,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Since the dew atop the blades of grass \Nhas been scattered by the winds,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.68,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:07.14,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I{\i0} hasn't been read yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:09.11,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,But she moved so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.72,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.61,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,She was faster than the child prodigy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.26,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Feel love deepen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:19.36,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,For you, I head out to the \Nfields to pick spring greens
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.95,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The sight of the lonely moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.87,Chiha-card-TS,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,makes me wonder how I ever\N let you fade from my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:23.87,Chiha-internal,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,A fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.75,Chiha-card-TS,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,covered by the smoky mountain fog
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:32.27,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,reminds me of the lonely \Ndawns after we parted
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:40.89,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Impassioned was your promise of salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.16,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ririka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.52,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to keep pushing yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:54.53,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Alas, another autumn has passed in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:17:03.17,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Rain takes longer to \Ndry in the autumn time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.40,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,If karuta's what you need...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.05,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to find \Nsomething you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:17.71,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Something that will \Nhelp you like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:22.10,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:28.28,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Her opponent's also holding back tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.61,Chiha-internal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.55,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She made it past the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:33.80,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:37.66,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:44.62,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give Chihaya-chan \Nas many weapons as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:47.17,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,She needs more than her game sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:50.63,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,She needs situational awareness, \Ntiming, accuracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:54.59,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing \Nin karuta is talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.21,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,but talent is never equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:01.51,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,She needs more than one weapon to use,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.39,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,so she doesn't find herself overwhelmed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.80,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,by prodigies, like the Queen \Nand the current Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.86,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chihaya-chan! \NGimme your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:19.24,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,This is my lucky mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:21.98,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.75,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ririka-chan couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.93,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,They said she was the \Nnext Wakamiya Shinobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.91,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,but she's not that talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:34.02,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the Queen is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.95,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair to compare them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.88,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:40.50,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.47,Chiha-main,Ririka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:48.30,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there was someone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.84,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,who first encouraged Ririka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:58.74,Chiha-flashback,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you have \Nthe talent for Karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:02.60,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a memory I've always treasured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.88,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone ruin that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.79,cellphone2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya made it through the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:14.19,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sudo-kun!  I lost!  I'm so upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:14.19,Chiha-overlap,A,0000,0000,0000,,The first round was tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.28,Chiha-overlap,B,0000,0000,0000,,Class A is completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:17.10,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were just \Nparticipating for the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:18.30,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:23.28,cellphone,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya made it through the first round.\N Good luck to you, Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:23.30,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm in Class A, I want \Nto try to become Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:27.93,cellphone3,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya made it through the first round.\N Good luck to you, Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.93,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I want to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:29.71,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.85,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to stuff your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.69,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty of chocolate left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.56,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,This?  You want this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:39.64,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't spill so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.65,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's not ladylike!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:47.58,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Murao-san lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:50.92,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, to a freshman from Seijo University.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.58,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody expected him to lose that match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.44,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Murao-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:58.39,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,made it to the final match against \Nthe Master two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.68,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't been practicing much, lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.58,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.37,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,You won your first match?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.55,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:17.21,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:20.68,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,The Nagumo society has a lot of members,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:23.67,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but there aren't many with the \Npotential to become Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.62,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be pinning \Ntheir hopes on you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.50,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,However, you'll never make it \Npast the role of challenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:31.87,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,The Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:35.15,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,Suo Hisashi can't be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.97,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Murao-san, Murao-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.56,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Play me next!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:45.39,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,Arata-kun, you've gotten really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:50.60,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,I need to become Master \Nbefore you catch up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:08.28,cellphone,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya made it through the first round.\NMy goal is to become the Eastern qualifier finalist,\Nso you better become the Western qualifier finalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.05,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The second round is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:12.63,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Will the players please move \Nto their assigned seats?
